{"tid":451610,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"四叔教你點由1萬變4.68億","createTime":"2017-10-29T11:35:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-02T05:56:31.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"4221ad7a5cc03e4b236426da43247b1da463dcc8","tid":451610,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T11:35:29.000Z","msg":"中環在線：四叔推個人網頁教錢滾錢<br />\n88歲嘅恒地（012）主席「四叔」李兆基真夠潮，噚日推出個人網頁。查實佢出過自傳，今次再推個人網頁，十足十係電子版自傳，佢同大家開心share好多同屋企人影嘅合照、金句、演講片段等等。<br />\n話明係個人網頁，入面當然有四叔嘅威水史，仲有大量「四叔金句」，仲記得四叔以前不時分享炒股心得與處世之道，近年佢少咗公開講，惟有喺佢網頁重溫一下。<br />\n話1萬可變4.68億<br />\n好似「男人最怕入錯行，女人最怕嫁錯郎」，佢認為入錯行好難翻身，如果順住個勢，好似近年投身金融業就可以變成富翁。此外，又有「搵錢要成功、使錢要成功」，呼籲大家賺錢之餘，不忘要多做慈善。最盞鬼莫過於佢叫後生仔要學識刻苦耐勞，如果經濟收入唔夠穩定就不宜早婚。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">四叔又教大家要識得錢滾錢，仲舉咗個例子解釋，假如由20歲起，有1萬蚊本金做生意，每月有2%利潤嘅話，息叠息下，50年後就會變成4.68億喇，不過，最緊要係有本先</span>。<br />\n網頁亦輯錄咗唔少四叔嘅演講，大家有興趣不妨收睇。聽聞四叔都好重視呢個網頁，從首頁嘅相片挑選同埋色調，四叔都有畀意見，話最緊要夠簡單同清楚。成個網頁由構思到設計再到資料搜集，足足籌備咗成年，真係落足工夫㗎。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20171024/20192820\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171024%2F20192820&d=XwQlyROJB9lzKPRASNs25hv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=0e4fce27\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171024%2F20192820&h=b168eb0e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20171024/20192820</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每月只需2%利潤 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd6a3c91163edc13b73b83eb19f36f64ec14b98b","tid":451610,"uid":89743,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T11:53:05.000Z","msg":"點計4.68億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d04f5f5c8452a98fbb3231b506c7a1ca263ecfa","tid":451610,"uid":18672,"like":32,"dislike":8,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T12:08:15.000Z","msg":"10000x1.02^600 = 1445782811"},{"pid":"fc42b351a07726c7bfdc9c69aae44652e75794f2","tid":451610,"uid":34530,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T12:26:18.000Z","msg":"如果係，銀行提早bankrupt"},{"pid":"72864c49fe403565e05363034c93c56580fe3695","tid":451610,"uid":59567,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T12:26:47.000Z","msg":"有乜公司一年可以27%利潤"},{"pid":"394719bb1cdf152a6d92c7d60a77be5c4ab18587","tid":451610,"uid":34765,"like":27,"dislike":4,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T12:34:36.000Z","msg":"每月2%唔難<br />\n<br />\n難在點樣可以keep50年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"556e8158d8313db37cfc208cf05b2d8b5ee223b3","tid":451610,"uid":44980,"like":80,"dislike":2,"score":78,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T12:44:35.000Z","msg":"鳩up其實唔難<br />\n難就難在有人信"},{"pid":"548b17105a7b801e2117ab099ad956b800387a57","tid":451610,"uid":7343,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T12:49:17.000Z","msg":"如果咁計<br />\n4叔身家而家應該多過700+4內銀巿值"},{"pid":"e30f2787d50c24438827cb7044e2199831d209bd","tid":451610,"uid":124537,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T12:59:54.000Z","msg":"我夠可以話 兑換到津巴布韋幣即刻搞掂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a0147784a59417c377be8de91b8caed2c1dc6a6","tid":451610,"uid":33422,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T13:05:49.000Z","msg":"係咪講緊geometric sequence,一個月一萬呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65ebbac18058e19d560921f3112d48c0da9a701c","tid":451610,"uid":26619,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T13:44:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每月2%唔難<br />\n<br />\n難在點樣可以keep50年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif